As the data shows, upon the insertion of Eve there are errors in SBBs (unlike
 the first part which had no errors).
 The percentages of errors for all sequence lengths are all close to 25%
 apart for the 17% errors which was recorded for 50 bits.
 
\begin_inset Note Note
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Using the simulation, it can be seen in 
\end_layout

\end_inset

Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
